---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import Lyrics from "@/layout/Lyrics.astro";
---

<Lyrics title="Falling Short">
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p>I don't think I have the heart to look my mother in her eyes</p>
        <p>and say "It will be ok" and that "We can figure this out"</p>
    </span>
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p>What kind of son am I? What kind of son am I?</p>
        <p>The kind that can't make change in his own mother's heart</p>
    </span>
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p>In this abscence</p>
        <p>During these tender years</p>
    </span>
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p>It's so hard to stand</p>
        <p>When these feet feel cold</p>
        <p>When these arms can't hold</p>
        <p>And these hands can't warm</p>
        <p>
            It's so hard to say the right things when there's nothing I
            could say
        </p>
        <p>With a heart that beats Oh, how hard it beats</p>
        <p>For you!</p>
    </span>
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p>I'm fallin short and I'm missing out</p>
        <p>But we'll find the courage</p>
    </span>
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p class="text-primary">It starts with us</p>
    </span>
    <span class="gap-y-2">
        <p>This heart is free from evil and malice</p>
        <p>And when things change...</p>
        <p>It will remain so</p>
    </span>
</Lyrics>
